# Design Token Quick Reference

Use these exact class names when styling components. NEVER use arbitrary values.

## Breakpoints

| Prefix | Range | When to Use |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| (none) | Base/mobile-first | Default styles |
| `mob:` | max-480px | Mobile-only overrides |
| `tab:` | 481px-1024px | Tablet-specific |
| `desk:` | 1025px-1600px | Desktop-specific |
| `fw:` | 1601px+ | Large screens (full width) |

