## Common Patterns

### Button with Focus State
```jsx
className="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-purple-DEFAULT text-white hover:bg-purple-dark focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-border focus:ring-offset-2 transition-colors"
```

### Responsive Text
```jsx
className="text-body-sm tab:text-body-md desk:text-body-lg"
```

### Responsive Heading
```jsx
className="text-h1-mob tab:text-h1-tab desk:text-h1-desk fw:text-h1"
```

### Conditional Classes
```jsx
import { cn } from '@/lib/cn';

className={cn(
  'base-classes',
  isActive && 'bg-purple-DEFAULT text-white',
  isDisabled && 'opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed'
)}
```

### Card Pattern
```jsx
className="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-md"
```

### Section Padding
```jsx
className="px-6 py-12 tab:px-10 tab:py-16 desk:px-37 desk:py-24"
```

## Styled-Components → Tailwind Mapping

| styled-components | Tailwind Equivalent |
|-------------------|---------------------|
| `${media.mobile} { ... }` | `mob:...` |
| `${media.tablet} { ... }` | `tab:...` |
| `${media.desktop} { ... }` | `desk:...` |
| `${media.fullWidth} { ... }` | `fw:...` |
| `${text.h1}` | `text-h1 font-archivo` |
| `${text.bodyLg}` | `text-body-lg font-archivo` |
| `${text.eyebrow}` | `text-eyebrow font-archivo` |
| `${colors.primaryPurple}` | `text-purple-DEFAULT` or `bg-purple-DEFAULT` |
| `${colors.primaryOrange}` | `text-orange-DEFAULT` or `bg-orange-DEFAULT` |
| `${colors.darkPurple}` | `text-purple-dark` or `bg-purple-dark` |
| `${colors.txtPrimary}` | `text-txt-primary` |
| `${colors.grey500}` | `text-grey-500` or `bg-grey-500` |
| `${props.theme.hero.bg}` | Use appropriate gradient: `bg-purple-orbital` |
